## 5. Controls

Main controls:

- `Space` — pause / resume;
- `1`–`8` — select simulation speed;
- `WASD` or arrow keys — move the camera;
- mouse wheel or `Q` / `E` — zoom;
- click a human — select a human;
- `Save` / `Load` buttons — save and load state.

